Download rcdaq-rikensuite

https://drive.google.com/file/d/16zWaowOpWldk8Ra0UtuWv3Qbvw6jl702/view?usp=sharing

- Making build and install directories

cd /home/wasabi/rcdaq-rikensuite/

mkdir build-rcdaq
mkdir install-rcdaq

cd build-rcdaq/

mkdir rcdaq

mkdir online_distribution
mkdir -p online_distribution/eventlibraries
mkdir -p online_distribution/pmonitor

mkdir -p online_distribution/eventlibraries
mkdir -p online_distribution/pmonitor

- Define an environmental variable ONLINE_MAIN

Add to .bashrc and also run command

#RCDAQ                                                                                    
export ONLINE_MAIN=/home/wasabi/rcdaq-rikensuite/install-rcdaq

export OFFLINE_MAIN=/home/wasabi/rcdaq-rikensuite/install-rcdaq

 

- Install rcdaq

cd rcdaq/

../../rcdaq-rikensuite/rcdaq/autogen.sh --prefix=$ONLINE_MAIN

make install

- Install online_distribution

Install lzo library: sudo yum  install lzo lzo-devel

Install boost library: sudo yum install boost boost-devel

Using root5 enviroinment

cd /home/wasabi/rcdaq-rikensuite/build-rcdaq/online_distribution/newbasic

../../../rcdaq-rikensuite/online_distribution/newbasic/autogen.sh --prefix=$ONLINE_MAIN

make install

cd /home/wasabi/rcdaq-rikensuite/build-rcdaq/online_distribution/pmonitor

../../../rcdaq-rikensuite/online_distribution/pmonitor/autogen.sh --prefix=$ONLINE_MAIN

make install

- Add to .bashrc

Add to .bashrc

#RCDAQ                                                                                   

PATH=$PATH:$ONLINE_MAIN/bin
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$ONLINE_MAIN/lib
source $ONLINE_MAIN/bin/aliases.sh
export ROOT_INCLUDE_PATH=$ONLINE_MAIN/include:$ONLINE_MAIN/include/Event:$ONLINE_MAIN/include/pmonitor

- Install CAENdrs

cd /home/wasabi/rcdaq-rikensuite/build-rcdaq/CAENdrs

../../rcdaq-rikensuite/CAENdrs/autogen.sh --prefix=$ONLINE_MAIN

make install

Got Errors

/usr/include/CAENVMEtypes.h:323:9: error: 'VARIANT_BOOL' does not name a type
         CAEN_BOOL cvDS0;      /* Data Strobe 0 signal    

Just modify /usr/include/CAENVMEtypes.h

//#ifdef LINUX
//#define CAEN_BYTE       unsigned char
//#define CAEN_BOOL       int
//#else
//#define CAEN_BYTE       byte
//#define CAEN_BOOL       VARIANT_BOOL
//#endif
#define CAEN_BYTE       unsigned char
#define CAEN_BOOL       int
 

Then do again: make install

- Compile simple online monitoring code

cd /home/wasabi/rcdaq-rikensuite/rcdaq-rikensuite/useranalysis/online1

make

- deactive/disable firewalld service to enable web access

systemctl stop firewalld

systemctl disable firewalld

